Synopsis: Modifies the primaryGroupId attribute of an object in a ntds.dit file.
Description: Modifies the primaryGroupId attribute of an account in a ntds.dit file. The most relevant group relative identifiers (RIDs) include 512 for Domain Admins , 513 for Domain Users , and 519 for Schema Admins .

Examples.Title: Example 1
Examples.Code:
PS C:\> Set-ADDBPrimaryGroup -SamAccountName John `
                             -PrimaryGroupId 512 `
                             -DatabasePath 'D:\Windows\NTDS\ntds.dit'
Moves the account John from the default Domain Users group to Domain Admins .
